00:39:15,000 --> 00:39:16,000
 -Talih dana.

471
00:39:16,000 --> 00:39:17,000
 -Da.

472
00:39:17,000 --> 00:39:18,000
 -Da.

473
00:39:18,000 --> 00:39:19,000
 -Da.

474
00:39:19,000 --> 00:39:20,000
 -Isto sam nešto.

