00:39:20,000 --> 00:39:21,000
 -Da.

476
00:39:21,000 --> 00:39:22,000
 -I tako.

477
00:39:22,000 --> 00:39:23,000
 Da.

478
00:39:23,000 --> 00:39:27,000
 Tu se ti, ja i slažemo, ljudi, probudite se, komunicirajte, susjed iste.

479
00:39:27,000 --> 00:39:28,000
 Nemojte te fore.

480
